==Useful Info==
'''Anacondas''' are extremely fast, non-venomous [[constriction|constricting]] snakes which deal significant damage in melee. They annihilate lightly-armoured casters foolish enough to let them get close, and are a risk to anyone else who can't kill them quickly. They can be found in some vaults (e.g. one of the possible endings of [[the Lair]]) and more commonly in [[the Snake Pits]].

==Tips & Tricks==
While anacondas do a lot of damage, they lack poison resistance. [[Curare]] [[dart]]s are quite effective. If it managed to get close and constrict you, you can always try [[Mephitic Cloud]]. Like other snakes, they have poor [[willpower]], so a [[wand of paralysis]] or the like will also work.

==History==
*In [[0.10]], anacondas got a bite attack. Previously, they could only constrict their enemies.
*Prior to [[0.7]], anacondas weren't amphibious.
